==Demographics==
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 Census]],<ref>{{Cite web |title=Explore Census Data |url=https://data.census.gov/profile?g=1600000US1929325 |access-date=2022-12-02 |website=data.census.gov}}</ref> there were 193 people and 74 total housing units in the community. The population density was {{convert|238.27|/mi2|/km2|disp=preunit|inhabitants&nbsp;|inhabitants|}}. The racial makeup of the city was 93.3% [[White people|White]], 0.5% [[African Americans|African American]], 1.0% [[Native Americans in the United States|Native American]], 1.0% [[Asian Americans|Asian]], 0.5% from other races, and 3.6% from two or more races. [[Hispanic]] or [[Latin America|Latino]] of any race were 3.6% of the population.

The median age in the city was 38.5 years.{{US Census population
